description: Over 60% reserved! Welcome home to Vantage Point - a collection of 30 well appointed homes in the heart of South Boston outfitted in the finest finishes. Unit 502 boasts 3 large bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms including a luxurious primary suite dripping in marble, designer lighting and plumbing fixtures. This penthouse front facing home has floor to ceiling windows allowing light to pour in while giving unobstructed city views. Open concept kitchen and living are perfect for hosting. The kitchen boasts two tone shaker cabinets, marble counters and Bosch stainless steel appliances. Plethora of closet space is found throughout this unit. Wide plank oak flooring, central heat/AC. Ideal South Boston location! Close to everything - bars, restaurants, coffee shops, retail, Seaport, public transportation. Professionally manage and 2 GARAGE parking included.
